==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: One foot high and one foot low.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: yī jiǎo gāo yī jiǎo dī

===Idiom===
'''[[一]][[腳]][[高]][[一]][[腳]][[低]]'''

# Describes an awkward way of walking.

===Alternate forms===
'''[[一脚高一脚低]]''' (Simplified Chinese)

